              "id": "968c6b87",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"79\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"79\">Janitorial &amp; Housekeeping Facility Services (for select commercial clients)</strong></h2><p data-start=\"81\" data-end=\"267\">Some facilities need more than exceptional floor care. They need a comprehensive, discreet, dependable partner who understands the demands of a premium property or high profile business.</p><p data-start=\"269\" data-end=\"458\">At Midland Floor Care, we provide exclusive janitorial and housekeeping facility services to select commercial clients who value consistency, confidentiality, and a higher standard of care.</p><p data-start=\"460\" data-end=\"496\"><strong data-start=\"460\" data-end=\"496\">What makes our service different</strong></p><ul data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"838\"><li data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"597\"><p data-start=\"499\" data-end=\"597\">Selective partnerships: we work with a limited number of clients for maximum attention and quality</p></li><li data-start=\"598\" data-end=\"668\"><p data-start=\"600\" data-end=\"668\">White glove standards: detail oriented service beyond industry norms</p></li><li data-start=\"669\" data-end=\"745\"><p data-start=\"671\" data-end=\"745\">Discreet, professional staff: fully trained, uniformed, background checked</p></li><li data-start=\"746\" data-end=\"838\"><p data-start=\"748\" data-end=\"838\">Flexible scope: from daily upkeep to specialized event preparation, tailored to your needs</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"840\" data-end=\"883\"><strong data-start=\"840\" data-end=\"883\">Services offered for our select clients</strong></p><ul data-start=\"884\" data-end=\"1302\"><li data-start=\"884\" data-end=\"971\"><p data-start=\"886\" data-end=\"971\">Full janitorial care: sweeping, mopping, dusting, trash removal, restroom maintenance</p></li><li data-start=\"972\" data-end=\"1050\"><p data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"1050\">Housekeeping services: common area upkeep, furniture dusting, glass cleaning</p></li><li data-start=\"1051\" data-end=\"1146\"><p data-start=\"1053\" data-end=\"1146\">Floor maintenance: integrated with our specialty programs for carpet, tile, and hard surfaces</p></li><li data-start=\"1147\" data-end=\"1229\"><p data-start=\"1149\" data-end=\"1229\">Special event prep and cleanup: guest ready before and after important occasions</p></li><li data-start=\"1230\" data-end=\"1302\"><p data-start=\"1232\" data-end=\"1302\">High touch disinfection: enhanced sanitation for high contact surfaces</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1304\" data-end=\"1354\"><strong data-start=\"1304\" data-end=\"1354\">Industries and facilities we serve exclusively</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1355\" data-end=\"1569\"><li data-start=\"1355\" data-end=\"1381\"><p data-start=\"1357\" data-end=\"1381\">Corporate headquarters</p></li><li data-start=\"1382\" data-end=\"1422\"><p data-start=\"1384\" data-end=\"1422\">Luxury hotels and hospitality venues</p></li><li data-start=\"1423\" data-end=\"1450\"><p data-start=\"1425\" data-end=\"1450\">Executive office suites</p></li><li data-start=\"1451\" data-end=\"1490\"><p data-start=\"1453\" data-end=\"1490\">Upscale retail stores and showrooms</p></li><li data-start=\"1491\" data-end=\"1535\"><p data-start=\"1493\" data-end=\"1535\">Private healthcare and medical practices</p></li><li data-start=\"1536\" data-end=\"1569\"><p data-start=\"1538\" data-end=\"1569\">High security government spaces</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1571\" data-end=\"1610\"><strong data-start=\"1571\" data-end=\"1610\">Why partner with Midland Floor Care</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1611\" data-end=\"1919\"><li data-start=\"1611\" data-end=\"1687\"><p data-start=\"1613\" data-end=\"1687\">Limited client list: your facility gets the focus and priority it deserves</p></li><li data-start=\"1688\" data-end=\"1774\"><p data-start=\"1690\" data-end=\"1774\">Comprehensive solutions: floor care, janitorial, and housekeeping under one provider</p></li><li data-start=\"1775\" data-end=\"1841\"><p data-start=\"1777\" data-end=\"1841\">Confidentiality assured: discretion in every client relationship</p></li><li data-start=\"1842\" data-end=\"1919\"><p data-start=\"1844\" data-end=\"1919\">Consistency guaranteed: same trusted team, same high standards, every visit</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1921\" data-end=\"2119\"><strong data-start=\"1921\" data-end=\"1950\">Schedule an on-site visit</strong><br />Ready to discuss your facility. <a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\">Schedule an on-site visit today.</a> Call us or request a visit online and we\u2019ll walk the space, build the plan, and align on your timeline.</p><p data-start=\"2121\" data-end=\"2215\">For facilities where presentation is everything, maintenance is not a task. It\u2019s a commitment.</p><p data-start=\"2217\" data-end=\"2245\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Thank you,<br data-start=\"2227\" data-end=\"2230\" />Justin Campbell</p><ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/floor-care-services/\">Services</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/about/\">About Midland</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/our-work-in-action/\">Our Work</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\">Schedule Your Visit & Quote</a></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/about/\">About Midland</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/floor-care-services/\">Services</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/schedule-a-visit/\">Schedule Your Visit &amp; Quote</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/7-essential-tips-for-impeccable-commercial-floor-care-services/\">7 Essential Tips for Impeccable Commercial Floor Care Services</a></li>\n</ul>",
                "align": "left",
